## Astro Configuration

Blueprint requires SSR configuration for @popperjs/core:

```javascript
// astro.config.mjs
export default defineConfig({
  vite: {
    ssr: {
      noExternal: [
        '@blueprintjs/core',
        '@blueprintjs/icons',
        '@blueprintjs/select',
        '@blueprintjs/table',
        '@blueprintjs/datetime',
        '@popperjs/core',
      ],
    },
  },
});
```

